    <h2>Reward Chart Guide for Parents</h2>
    <p>A reward chart can make everyday routines easier for children to understand, practice, and repeat. Used well, it is not a bribe. It is a simple visual tool that helps your child see progress, feel proud, and build one small habit at a time.</p>
